title: Wolf (disambiguation)
content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Wolf (disambiguation)

Wolf may refer to:

  • Wolf (Soul Wars), the monster found in the Soul Wars minigame.
  • Wolves, canine enemies that can be found in various places with varying combat levels (11, 14, 25, and 64).
  • Big Wolf, a level 73 wolf that leads packs of other wolves at the zenith of White Wolf Mountain.
  • Desert Wolf, a wolf in the Kharidian Desert.
  • Dire wolf, a wolf found in Tirannwn.
  • Ice wolf, a wolf found on the Ice Path during Desert Treasure, the top of Trollweiss Mountain, and near the entrance of God Wars Dungeon.
  • Jungle wolf, a wolf found in the Kharazi Jungle.
  • White wolves, wolves located on top of White Wolf Mountain.
  • Werewolves, found in Canifis when players attack the humans residing there without wielding the Wolfbane dagger.


 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
